install kylin
-------------
0.sudo -u hdfs hadoop fs -chmod -R 777 / (DON'T DO THIS AT HOME)
1.wget http://apache.rediris.es/kylin/apache-kylin-1.5.4.1/apache-kylin-1.5.4.1-cdh5.7-bin.tar.gz
2.tar -zxvf apache-kylin-1.5.4.1-cdh5.7-bin.tar.gz 
3.pwd
4.export KYLIN_HOME = /home/clouderaadmin/kylin/apache-kylin-1.5.4.1-cdh5.7-bin
5.Abrir puertos en VM
6. ./check-env.sh
Si todo ha ido bien:
7: ./kylin.sh start

